data.description: Leyden Rock stunner!! Situated on a quiet street at the top of the Leyden Rock subdivision in West Arvada, this four bedroom, four bathroom home lives like a model home with an abundance of upgrades. Walk into an wide open floorplan with vaulted ceilings, a large dining space and stunningly modern kitchen fixtures including a double oven, counter depth refrigerator, and large walk in pantry. A gorgeous guest suite completes the main level. Head upstairs to an open loft space, two spacious bedrooms with a shared jack and jill bathroom and a primary suite with an upgraded electric fireplace, large bathroom and walk in closet. An upstairs laundry completes the second level. The basement is ready for your customization with over 1500SF of open space. An attached 3 car tandem garage offers the ability to store all of your toys and lawn equipment. Head to the covered patio in the backyard for the ultimate entertaining space, complete with custom landscaping. The community offers a beautiful pool, three parks and miles of trails. Conveniently located close to Boulder, Golden and Arvada.
